{
  "id": "RAW_eda34f",
  "title": "ChatGPT 记忆增强，AI 更懂我了！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/0dHVWbx72k_S7pmG4rqbNg",
  "date": "2025-04-10 21:54:35",
  "author": "lencx",
  "siteName": "浮之静",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote style=\"margin-left:0;padding:0.5rem 1em;margin:0;color:#888;border-left:.25em solid #dfe2e5;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;margin-top:0;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:0;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sam 兴奋地睡不着，我还以为 OpenAI 又有啥大动作，谁知几个小时过去了，只看到了一个记忆增强功能。虽然发布了，却又差</span><s style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(206, 60, 60);\"><span leaf=\"\">很多</span></s><span leaf=\"\">点意思...</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"385\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006284\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/43a5dd11-50f4-46a7-2a99-5527f6086400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/43a5dd11-50f4-46a7-2a99-5527f6086400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sam 原帖：一年里总有那么几次，我会因为要发布一个期待已久的新功能而在清晨兴奋地醒来，怎么也睡不着。今天就是这样的一天！</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"255\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006285\" data-ratio=\"0.440536013400335\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0a47a3bf-2d28-43ff-fda5-2477fb9a6e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1194\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0a47a3bf-2d28-43ff-fda5-2477fb9a6e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 32px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: linear-gradient(transparent 50%, rgba(181, 181, 181, 0.5) 0px);padding: 0px 10px;font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆功能</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 记忆功能可以引用你所有的过往聊天记录，提供更个性化的回复——基于你的喜好和兴趣，为写作、获取建议、学习等带来更多帮助。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006287\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250411060605_517d5e\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250411060605_517d5e\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了此前已有的保存记忆功能之外，它现在能够参考你过去的聊天记录，给出更贴合、有用的回复。新的对话会自然而然地建立在它对你的了解之上，让交互更加流畅，并为你量身打造独特的体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">和往常一样，你可以完全掌控 ChatGPT 的记忆功能。你可以随时在设置中选择退出引用过去聊天记录或完全关闭记忆。如果你原先已经关闭了记忆功能，那么默认也不会引用过去的聊天记录。如果想修改 ChatGPT 对你的了解，只需在聊天中直接提出即可。如果想进行一次不使用或影响记忆的对话，也可使用临时聊天。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"415\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006288\" data-ratio=\"0.71796875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23ea3151-4aa3-4a2b-0fbb-ad3fde66c000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23ea3151-4aa3-4a2b-0fbb-ad3fde66c000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆功能的最新改进从即日起，逐步向所有 Plus 和 Pro 用户推出，但不包括欧盟经济区（EEA）、英国、瑞士、挪威、冰岛和列支敦士登地区。团队版、企业版和教育版用户将在几周后获得使用权限。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你在 ChatGPT 中看到以下提示时，就表示已经获得了改进后的记忆功能：</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"381\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006289\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05cbcbcd-08c6-4efc-939e-3a40706e1c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05cbcbcd-08c6-4efc-939e-3a40706e1c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">额...，这次的记忆功能很难评价。感觉产生了两部分极端人群。喜欢的特别喜欢，认为 AI 更懂自己了，可以更好地交流。讨厌的人则认为 OpenAI 这是在将用户数据绑定在平台。还有一些人表示这种体验很差，认为在 ChatGPT 里有许多对话并没有特定意义，比较发散，让其成为记忆会十分凌乱。还有一些人不太敢相信这就是全部的更新，有点糊弄人了。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"404\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006290\" data-ratio=\"0.69921875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2250c9ea-a580-454f-2c4e-856fc0ba0200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2250c9ea-a580-454f-2c4e-856fc0ba0200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">也有一些有趣评论，项目太多，把 ChatGPT 搞懵逼了。人工智能不仅助我学习，更助力我蜕变！</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"334\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006291\" data-ratio=\"0.57734375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0272b60-923c-4424-6300-44fd3cd89b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0272b60-923c-4424-6300-44fd3cd89b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有用户表示开启记忆后，回复变迟钝，还会翻老垃圾了 😅（扎心了，看来记太多也不是件好事）...</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"832\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006292\" data-ratio=\"1.4394785847299814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c65e1743-6240-43fb-05fb-51330900ff00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1074\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c65e1743-6240-43fb-05fb-51330900ff00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">评论区还看到一张关于 “Internal knowledge” 的截图，大概率也是这次更新的内容。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"544\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006293\" data-ratio=\"0.9413735343383585\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7975dbfa-e21c-48be-2bd6-932bf0bea200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1194\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7975dbfa-e21c-48be-2bd6-932bf0bea200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 32px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: linear-gradient(transparent 50%, rgba(181, 181, 181, 0.5) 0px);padding: 0px 10px;font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp</span></span></h1>\n  <blockquote style=\"margin-left:0;padding:0.5rem 1em;margin:0;color:#888;border-left:.25em solid #dfe2e5;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;margin-top:0;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:0;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">除改进的记忆功能外，OpenAI 还发布了一个评测基准。基准内容没太大意思，感兴趣的可以去看原文。不过针对 GPT 系列模型的测评结果还是挺有趣的，可以指导我们更好地使用 ChatGPT。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006295\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5f85a90c-6e64-4b55-de3a-74e46ad0db00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5f85a90c-6e64-4b55-de3a-74e46ad0db00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(64, 134, 208);text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">（检验浏览代理能力的评测基准）：随着 AI 代理在互联网浏览与知识获取方面的应用日趋广泛，高效的浏览代理必须能够搜寻并整合难以获取的信息，往往需要访问几十甚至上百个网站。现有的基准（如主要考察检索基本孤立事实的 SimpleQA）已经无法充分区分这些代理的优劣，比如具备浏览功能的 GPT-4o 在此类简单任务中几乎达到上限。为了评估 AI 代理在互联网中定位复杂、纠缠信息的真实能力，OpenAI 推出了一个名为 BrowseComp（“Browsing Competition”）的新基准，共包含 1,266 道难度较高的问题。该基准已经在 OpenAI 的&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(64, 134, 208);text-decoration: none;\"><span leaf=\"\">simple-evals</span><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(16, 163, 127);font-weight: bold;font-size: 0.7rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></sup></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;GitHub 项目中开源，并配套了研究论文供参考。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 24px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.35rem;display: inline-block;height: 100%;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);padding: 8px 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">评测对象与结果</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 将以下模型应用于 BrowseComp 进行测试：</span></p>\n  <ol style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-4o、GPT-4.5</span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（均不具备浏览功能）</span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: 0.25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI o1</span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（中等体量，不具备浏览功能，但推理能力相对较强）</span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: 0.25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-4o（带浏览功能）</span></strong></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: 0.25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Deep Research</span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（经过专门训练，能够进行持续网页浏览的代理模型）</span></span></li>\n  </ol>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. GPT-4o 和 GPT-4.5</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不具备浏览功能，准确率几乎为零，说明在需要多步推理或跨多个站点查找信息时，单纯依靠内部知识和有限推理无法应对 BrowseComp 的复杂问题。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. GPT-4o（带浏览功能）</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">启用浏览后，准确率从 0.6% 提高到 1.9%，虽然有所提升，但整体仍较低。事实表明，仅具备浏览能力远远不够，模型还需要具备战略性推理思维，能够发现合适的搜索路径，并准确理解检索到的内容。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. OpenAI o1</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然没有浏览功能，但在推理能力上胜过 GPT-4o，准确率明显更高。这表明一部分问题可以直接通过内部推理来解答，而无需在线信息。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.25rem;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. Deep Research</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在所有模型中表现最佳，能解答大约一半的问题。它具备持续搜索、多源信息整合以及自适应搜索策略等特性，能够高效解决许多跨站点、多跳检索的复杂问题。通过整合大量在线信息，并在搜索过程中根据检索结果进行调整，Deep Research 尤其擅长处理那些内容小众、答案不直观且需要多网站交叉验证的题目——这些正是 BrowseComp 想要重点考查的难点。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 24px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 1.35rem;display: inline-block;height: 100%;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(88, 88, 88);padding: 8px 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">小结</span></span></h2>\n  <ul style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;padding-left: 2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp</span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;与传统基准不同，专门针对难以检索、多步推理的问题设计。</span></span></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: 0.25em;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">测试结果显示，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">浏览能力与推理能力同等重要</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">；仅有浏览工具难以明显提高准确率，但若缺乏足够的推理能力，也难以利用浏览信息。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;word-break: break-all;margin-top: 0.25em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Deep Research</span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;将自主浏览与复杂推理结合，能在此高难度基准上实现显著领先的表现。</span></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">总体而言，BrowseComp 有效地考验了 AI 代理在互联网中定位稀有信息、灵活调整搜索路径以及综合多方信息的能力，为后续提升浏览型 AI 模型的研发提供了重要参考。</span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 32px;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;font-weight: 600;line-height: 1.25;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: linear-gradient(transparent 50%, rgba(181, 181, 181, 0.5) 0px);padding: 0px 10px;font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">爆料</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">公开的更新内容虽然有点少，但有人在最新版 ChatGPT 网页源代码中发现了新增的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"color: rgb(64, 134, 208);padding: 0px 3px;border-radius: 2px;font-size: 15px;word-break: break-word;background-color: rgba(115, 183, 225, 0.1);box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">o4-mini</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"color: rgb(64, 134, 208);padding: 0px 3px;border-radius: 2px;font-size: 15px;word-break: break-word;background-color: rgba(115, 183, 225, 0.1);box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">o4-mini-high</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"color: rgb(64, 134, 208);padding: 0px 3px;border-radius: 2px;font-size: 15px;word-break: break-word;background-color: rgba(115, 183, 225, 0.1);box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">o3</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;模型选项。感兴趣的朋友可自行查看源码&nbsp;</span><code style=\"color: rgb(64, 134, 208);padding: 0px 3px;border-radius: 2px;font-size: 15px;word-break: break-word;background-color: rgba(115, 183, 225, 0.1);box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://cdn.oaistatic.com/assets/o5mi5e8rf3i1o1na.js</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"472\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006296\" data-ratio=\"0.81640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/afa13d86-9483-4aaf-9571-18664addf700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/afa13d86-9483-4aaf-9571-18664addf700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"740\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100006297\" data-ratio=\"1.2806691449814127\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/34b6b1ef-adea-4ab6-4b72-7179f0c0be00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1076\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/34b6b1ef-adea-4ab6-4b72-7179f0c0be00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;border-top: 1px dashed rgb(216, 216, 216);padding-top: 20px;margin-top: 30px;color: rgb(104, 104, 104);font-size: 20px;font-weight: 300;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">References</span></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0px;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">BrowseComp:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://openai.com/index/browsecomp</span></em></p></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;margin: 3px 0px;width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;min-width: 40px;max-width: 40px;background: none;opacity: 0.6;margin-right: 5px;font-family: ptima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></span>\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);word-break: break-all;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: normal;margin-right: 4px;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">simple-evals:</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);word-break: break-all;font-weight: 300;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://github.com/openai/simple-evals</span></em></p></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文解读 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 记忆增强功能和 BrowseComp 基准评测，揭示 AI 模型在复杂信息检索上的局限，并爆料 OpenAI 潜在的新模型发布计划。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文解读 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 记忆增强功能和 BrowseComp 基准评测，揭示 AI 模型在复杂信息检索上的局限，并爆料 OpenAI 潜在的新模型发布计划。",
  "summary": "文章对 OpenAI 最新发布的 ChatGPT 记忆增强功能进行了详细解读，分析了该功能的特点、用户反馈以及潜在的隐私问题。同时，介绍了 OpenAI 推出的用于评估 AI 代理浏览能力的 BrowseComp 基准评测，对比了不同模型在该基准上的表现，揭示了现有 AI 模型在复杂信息检索和推理方面的局限性，强调了浏览能力与推理能力对 AI 代理的重要性。此外，文章还爆料了 ChatGPT 网页源代码中新增的 o4-mini、o4-mini-high 和 o3 模型选项，为读者提供了更全面的信息。",
